Analyzing and Visualizing Logs:
Once your application logs are flowing into Sumo Logic, you can take advantage of its robust analytics and visualization features to gain insights. Here's how:
Search and query: Sumo Logic offers a powerful search and query language that allows you to explore your logs using keywords, filters, and aggregations. Leverage this functionality to identify patterns, troubleshoot issues, or perform ad-hoc analysis.

Dashboards and alerts: Create custom dashboards to visualize key metrics, trends, or anomalies in your application logs. Configure alerts to get notified when specific log conditions are met, ensuring proactive monitoring and issue resolution.

